headline: Extra Space Storage Inc. Announces 1st Quarter 2026 Dividend
summary: Extra Space Storage Inc. (the "Company") (NYSE: EXR) announced today that the Company's board of directors has declared a first quarter 2026 dividend of $1.62 per share on the common stock of the Company. The dividend is payable on March 31, 2026, to stockholders of record at the close of business on March 16, 2026.

headline: Public Storage Beats Q4 FFO & Revenue Estimates, Unveils Initiatives
summary: PSA tops Q4 FFO and revenue estimates, launches its PS4.0 strategy and issues a 2026 outlook amid mixed same-store trends and expansion plans.
